description: Registers a new agent with AWS Ground Station.

parameters.name: agentDetails
parameters.description: Detailed information about the agent being registered. agentCpuCores (list) --- List of CPU cores reserved for the agent. (integer) --- Current agent version. List of versions being used by agent components. (dict) --- Version information for agent components. Component type. List of versions. (string) --- ID of EC2 instance agent is running on. Type of EC2 instance agent is running on. reservedCpuCores (list) --- List of CPU cores reserved for processes other than the agent running on the EC2 instance. (integer) ---

nested_params.name: agentCpuCores
nested_params.description: List of CPU cores reserved for the agent.

nested_params.name: componentVersions
nested_params.description: List of versions being used by agent components.

nested_params.name: instanceId
nested_params.description: ID of EC2 instance agent is running on.

nested_params.name: instanceType
nested_params.description: Type of EC2 instance agent is running on.

nested_params.name: reservedCpuCores
nested_params.description: List of CPU cores reserved for processes other than the agent running on the EC2 instance.

parameters.name: discoveryData
parameters.description: Data for associating an agent with the capabilities it is managing. List of capabilities to associate with agent. (string) --- List of private IP addresses to associate with agent. (string) --- List of public IP addresses to associate with agent. (string) ---

nested_params.name: capabilityArns
nested_params.description: List of capabilities to associate with agent.

nested_params.name: privateIpAddresses
nested_params.description: List of private IP addresses to associate with agent.

nested_params.name: publicIpAddresses
nested_params.description: List of public IP addresses to associate with agent.
